        {
          "name": "yn-dropdown",
          "description": "下拉浮层：触发器为默认插槽，面板为 `panel` 插槽。\n---\n\n\n### **Events:**\n - **open-change**\n\n### **Methods:**\n \n\n- **close()** - 供外部 JS 调用的关闭方法。\n- **render()** - 渲染触发器、关闭图标与内容面板。",
          "doc-url": "",
          "attributes": [
            {
              "name": "placement",
              "description": "面板相对触发器的位置。\n\n**可选值：**\n- `top-start` — 上方 · 左对齐\n- `top` — 上方 · 居中\n- `top-end` — 上方 · 右对齐\n- `bottom-start` — 下方 · 左对齐（默认）\n- `bottom` — 下方 · 居中\n- `bottom-end` — 下方 · 右对齐\n- `left-start` — 左侧 · 上对齐\n- `left` — 左侧 · 居中\n- `left-end` — 左侧 · 下对齐\n- `right-start` — 右侧 · 上对齐\n- `right` — 右侧 · 居中\n- `right-end` — 右侧 · 下对齐",
              "value": {
                "type": [
                  "top-start",
                  "top",
                  "top-end",
                  "bottom-start",
                  "bottom",
                  "bottom-end",
                  "left-start",
                  "left",
                  "left-end",
                  "right-start",
                  "right",
                  "right-end"
                ],
                "default": "\"bottom-start\""
