        {
          "name": "yn-pull-cord-switch",
          "description": "抽绳开关：下拉绳端切换开/关。支持 `fixed` 吸顶、`glow-up` 顶灯上扩；默认/activated 插槽放绳端按钮。\n---\n\n\n### **Events:**\n - **fixed-move** - `fixed` 模式下水平拖拽结束，`detail: { x, reverse }`\n- **change** - 开关变化，`detail.checked` 为当前状态\n\n### **Slots:**\n - _default_ - 关闭态绳端内容（如 `yn-button`）\n- **activated** - 开启态绳端内容",
          "doc-url": "",
          "attributes": [
            {
              "name": "checked",
              "description": "是否开启（绳端处于拉开/ON 状态）。",
              "value": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "default": "false"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "glow-up",
              "description": "开启且 checked 时，顶灯光向锚点上方对称扩散（默认仅向下）。",
              "value": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "default": "false"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "disabled",
              "description": "禁用拖拽与切换。",
              "value": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "default": "false"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "fixed",
              "description": "吸附视口；配合 `fixed-x`、`top` 定位。",
              "value": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "default": "false"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "reverse",
              "description": "`fixed-x` 是否自视口右侧起算。",
              "value": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "default": "false"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "variant",
              "description": "绳/卡片视觉主题。\n\n**可选值：**\n- `default` — 深色工业风（默认）\n- `floema` — 浅色 Floema 风",
              "value": {
                "type": [
                  "default",
                  "floema"
                ],
                "default": "\"default\""
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "size",
              "description": "绳端卡片与绳粗细（不控制绳长）。\n\n**可选值：**\n- `mini` — 最小（默认）\n- `small` — 小号\n- `medium` — 中号",
              "value": {
                "type": [
                  "mini",
                  "small",
                  "medium"
                ],
                "default": "\"mini\""
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "rope-length",
              "description": "绳身长度（px），与 `size` 解耦，默认 260。",
              "value": {
                "type": "string",
                "default": "DEFAULT_ROPE_LENGTH"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "fixed-x",
              "description": "水平偏移（px，可负）；未设则居中。",
              "value": {
                "type": "number | undefined"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "top",
              "description": "距视口顶部（px，可负）；仅 fixed 时有效。",
              "value": {
                "type": "number | undefined"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "toggle-threshold",
              "description": "下拉切换阈值（px）；未设则随绳长缩放。",
              "value": {
                "type": "number | undefined"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "card-offset",
              "description": "绳端卡片距绳头间距（px，可为负）。",
              "value": {
                "type": "number | undefined"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "z-index",
              "description": "叠放层级（写入 CSS 变量）。",
              "value": {
                "type": "number",
                "default": "1"
              }
            }
          ],
          "slots": [
            {
              "name": "",
              "description": "关闭态绳端内容（如 `yn-button`）"
            },
            {
              "name": "activated",
              "description": "开启态绳端内容"
